rComments: Textbook was useless but his lectures were good. Tests are fair and very easy if you pay attention in class.

Prof Trippen always gives hints and helpful questions to students so they have a great chance of getting high marks. His teaching style is easily understandable, clearly explains concepts, and answers any questions. He cares about every individual succeeding in his class. I would take any class with this professor, he is so genuine and nice.
Very nice prof, doesn't make students feel worthless.

He is an amazing professor, very considerate of his students and their problems. Changes due dates if students are struggling. Very sweet down to earth
